casebody.data:
Eileen CAPOZZI, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Michael KILENSKI and Tracy Kilenski, Defendants-Respondents. C-1040 September Term 2017
081080 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 20, 2018 To tha Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004155-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
